Figs 1B, C
, 
2C
). Collar shield divided transversally into three nearly rectangular sections with lateral margins indented (
Fig. 2B
). A pair of white triangular glandular pads in the ventral side of collar, as lung-shaped. Shields from chaetigers 2 to 8 rectangular, broad, entire (
